# ============================================
# SDR Station Capture Schedule - KiwiSDR Version
# All captures use KiwiSDR (zero OpenWebRX downtime!)
# Freq in kHz (not Hz) for KiwiSDR
# ============================================

# --- WEATHER FAX - NMC Point Reyes ---
